  "remarks": "He was sentenced to 15 years in prison in Indonesia in January 2022. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 8\n                Jun. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded\n                on 7 June 2018. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was\n                concluded on 15 November 2021. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
